<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Ram 第三方许可证 / Ram third-party licenses</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; margin: 2rem auto; max-width: 70rem; padding: 0 1rem; }
    pre { border: 1px solid #888; max-height: 24rem; overflow: auto; padding: 1rem; white-space: pre-wrap; }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) { body { background: #202124; color: #eee; } a { color: #8ab4f8; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <h1>Ram 第三方许可证 / <span lang="en">Ram third-party licenses</span></h1>
    <p>本报告由 x86-64 与 ARM64 Linux 发布目标的 Rust 锁定普通/构建依赖并集生成。<br>
      <span lang="en">This report is generated from the union of locked normal/build dependencies for the x86-64 and ARM64 Linux release targets.</span>
    </p>
    <h2>许可证概览 / <span lang="en">License overview</span></h2>
    <ul>
      {{#each overview}}
      <li>{{name}} ({{count}})</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>
    <h2>许可证正文 / <span lang="en">License texts</span></h2>
    {{#each licenses}}
    <section>
      <h3 data-spdx-id="{{id}}">{{name}}</h3>
      <p>使用方 / <span lang="en">Used by:</span></p>
      <ul>
        {{#each used_by}}
        <li><a href="{{#if crate.repository}}{{crate.repository}}{{else}}https://crates.io/crates/{{crate.name}}{{/if}}">{{crate.name}} {{crate.version}}</a></li>
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
      <pre>{{text}}</pre>
    </section>
    {{/each}}
  </main>
</body>
</html>
